##Pseudo Code for rotation

PROGRAM: PowerUpRotation  
  Load programme  
  Assign image to file pick  
  Create canvas  
  Import the image to the canvas in the center position  
  Display image  
  
  IF user presses space bar:
    Scale pixels inwards into negative of original position  
    Scale pixels outwards to give appearance of 2D rotation  
    
  IF user presses escape:
    Close program
  END.
